reviewText: My dad is in this movie. A scene was shot at a video rental store, ran by a chubby mustaches man named Guido. That's my dad, Tony Giglio. He passed in 2010 from cancer. Miss him every day
classic what more can i say. i wacth this ova a buddys house he bought a 80 horrors film set and this was in itand i thought was a classic movie ya know
